data.title: Dean’s List
data.meta_description: We publicly recognize our students’ superior academic achievements each semester through the Dean’s List.
data.text:
Congratulations & Great Work!

We publicly recognize our students’ superior academic achievements each semester through the Dean’s List. The Dean’s List is an honor reserved for students who earn at least 9 credits with a 3.5 GPA (Grade Point Average) or higher for the semester. The Dean’s List is published 6 weeks after the end of the term.

Congratulations to everyone who earned a place on the list! #gowoodducks
